Uses of Class
com.ibm.dragonfly.SqlDirective

    • Uses of SqlDirective in com.ibm.dragonfly

      Subclasses of SqlDirective in com.ibm.dragonfly 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      (package private) class  InsertRows
      This class represents a insertRows directive which inserts sub-templates at bookmarks for each row of the SQL result set.
      (package private) class  ReplaceColumn
      This class represents a replaceColumn directive which loads the Replace hashmap with the values of a "from" and "to" column in a sql result set.
      (package private) class  ReplaceRow
      This class represents a replaceRow directive which loads the Replace hashmap with the values of "{columnName}" to column.Value in a single row sql result set.
